. - (By leave)
- In appointing members to the Royal Commissions dealing with Navigation and National 'Insurance, the Government experienced considerable trouble in its endeavours to give representation to the different parties, and, as far as possible, to the States. The members have now been appointed. On the Royal Commission dealing with Navigation, they will be -
